  explosion.innerHTML = `
<span class="fail">💥 FAILURES DETECTED:</span>
• Subtotal displayed: <span class="warn">$${subtotal}</span>
  → Should be: <span class="pass">$${(14.99*2 + 8.49*3 + 6.99 + 3.49*4 + 2.99).toFixed(2)}</span>
• Tax displayed: <span class="warn">$${tax}</span>
