• Total displayed: <span class="warn">$${total}</span>
  → Should be: <span class="pass">$${((14.99*2 + 8.49*3 + 6.99 + 3.49*4 + 2.99)*(1+TAX_RATE)).toFixed(2)}</span>
• Discount threshold check: <span class="fail">BROKEN</span> (=== never fires correctly)
